<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:272px;"><a href="/wiki/File:SaoPaulo_PrestesMaia.jpg" class="image" title="Urban land use is often dominated by automobiles. Pictured: São Paulo, Brazil."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/9d/SaoPaulo_PrestesMaia.jpg/270px-SaoPaulo_PrestesMaia.jpg" width="270" height="202" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
